        <h3>The story of the Bodge üî®</h3>
        <p>
          It&apos;s been exactly three years since I first made that post on the Class of 2020 Facebook group &mdash; a little nervous since I&apos;m usually a private person, but also excited to share what I made with everyone.
          No more than a hastily
          <a href="https://youtu.be/lIFE7h3m40U" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">bodged-together</a> {{!Tom Scott&apos;s Art of the Bodge}}
          app for me to check my own meal balances, it became obvious that this could be put to use for many more people.
          In a quiet little house in the suburbs of Houston, where I was visiting a friend over Spring Break in 2017, I got to work polishing it up, that it was pretty enough for publication.
        </p>
